Column position in the query can be used as an alternative to column name in ORDER BY clause

QUERRY:
Select ID, ENAME, DOJ, SALARY, DEPT, DESIGNATION FROM Employee ORDER BY 2
5 row(s) selected
ID	ENAME	DOJ	SALARY	DEPT	DESIGNATION
5	Ayaz Mohammad	01-Apr-14	40000	ICP	TA
3	Emily Rayner	01-Jan-14	25000	ETA	SE
2	Ethan McCarty	01-Feb-14	90000	ETA	PM
4	Jack Abraham	01-Jul-14	30000	ETA	SSE
1	James Potter	01-Jun-14	75000	ICP	PM
The result is sorted alphabetically by name which appears at second position in the result.
